{"tid":1288111,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"有關嘲笑辱罵跳軌自殺死者","createTime":"2019-07-05T13:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T14:04:38.000Z","uid":59855,"like":14,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0554ac60aa1cf7bca43da95f12d78f8734304a5c","tid":1288111,"uid":59855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:07:50.000Z","msg":"題目 : 唉，屌你老母，想死去跳樓啦，跳乜撚野軌姐<br />\n時間 : 2018 年 9 月 7 日<br />\nLINK : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/808895/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/808895/page/1</a><br />\n2000 正評<br />\n<br />\n人若生前不是大奸大惡, 死者為大, 尊重死者乃道德基本, 此 POST 內文多番出現會員嘲笑及辱罵死者, 並獲 2000 正評支持發文者<br />\n本人對此等不道德行為十分不齒<br />\n懇請連黎住或管理團隊呼籲有關辱罵死者會員向死者道歉<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n自殺事件並非網絡潮文玩笑, 附明報新聞為証 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20180907/s00001/1536278231006/太和站凌晨男子墮軌亡-東鐵列車一度受阻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20180907%2Fs00001%2F1536278231006%2F%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E7%AB%99%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E8%BB%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E6%9D%B1%E9%90%B5%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=9d441136\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20180907%2Fs00001%2F1536278231006%2F%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E7%AB%99%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E8%BB%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E6%9D%B1%E9%90%B5%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB&h=a94a5bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20180907/s00001/1536278231006/太和站凌晨男子墮軌亡-東鐵列車一度受阻</a>"},{"pid":"73f900eb6378b9b46a76e9f6c5ecbeb7e17591ed","tid":1288111,"uid":12034,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"開成6,7個post都無人回 就收收皮先啦"},{"pid":"d97efa40f67c801c6a35b6508cabdeb3b5c3bd98","tid":1288111,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score"